    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 128,
    "rowsha": "bsmUG+b5aW4KvLXX47MM9BWrQWLDbyd4W3pq2Rx9XcM=",
    "originContent": "*WhatsApp from the airport:* \"Ship the auth refactor.\"",
    "translatedContent": "*واتساب من المطار:* \"انشر إعادة هيكلة المصادقة.\""
  },
  {
    "row": 129,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "3CJCJCHBsYgvlgwsy0T+iijoYPrqO0oNjXhej8sjw+4=",
    "originContent": "CORE already knows the branch, the context, and your preferences. It is running in Railway. It kicks off the session before you board.",
    "translatedContent": "CORE يعرف بالفعل الفرع والسياق وتفضيلاتك. يعمل على Railway. يبدأ الجلسة قبل أن تصعد للطائرة."
  },
  {
